Enum SkyRenderElement.CONSTELLATION_CONTOUR

    SkyRenderElement

    public static enum SkyRenderElement.CONSTELLATION_CONTOUR
extends java.lang.Enum<SkyRenderElement.CONSTELLATION_CONTOUR>
    The set of options to draw constellation contours. All values here except the default set of lines are derived from the GPL work by Jason Harris and Clemens ?, included in KStars. This selection also affects the labels for constellation names.
